org.danja.feedreader.interpreters

Class Rss1Handler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.danja.feedreader.interpreters.FeedHandlerBase
      • org.danja.feedreader.interpreters.Rss1Handler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeedHandler, org.xml.sax.ContentHandler

    public class Rss1Handler
extends FeedHandlerBase
    SAX2 handler for RSS 1.0 XML

    Populates a Feed object (with any contained items etc.). Is naive : treats RSS 1.0 as non-RDF XML, ignoring namespaces.

    Elements handled : webMaster, author, creator, guid, title, "pubDate", "link", "description"

    HTML content has a little cleaning/normalization, and links are pulled out of there too.

    See Also:
    XMLReaderParser, Feed, Entry, Person, DateStamp, Link
